2003-09-05  Adam Hooper <adamh@densi.com>
	* ephy-gestures.xml:

	Added an up-right-down gesture for 'View Source' because Firebird's
	gestures allow it and it's a lot easier than an "S." Firebird has plenty
	of gestures we still don't support, but I personally never see a need to
	use 'em :P. The full list is at
	http://optimoz.mozdev.org/gestures/defaultmappings.html.

